Class JobEventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revature.sms.domain.JobEventType

  • @Entity
public class JobEventType
extends java.lang.Object
    Object that represents the Job Event Type. Mostly for use as part of a JobEvent object, and to follow normalization principles in the database.
